Package solver.analysis.enemyprobability

Class SingleEnemyPrediction

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.analysis.enemyprobability.SingleEnemyPrediction
  • public class SingleEnemyPrediction
extends Object
    Calculates the enemy forward prediction for a single IPlayer. Done by calculating the probabilities of the enemy location based on his valid actions with a certain recursive search depth. Then flood filling is performed for the minimum steps.
